://dbpedia.org/resource/Disney's_Caribbean_Beach_Resort\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disney's_Caribbean_Beach_Resort\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tobago - Special Olympics\", \"from\": 28, \"to\": 53}, {\"ngram\": \"Trinidad\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 62}, {\"ngram\": \"Tobago\", \"from\": 67, \"to\": 73}, {\"ngram\": \"(SOTT\", \"from\": 74, \"to\": 79}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 110, \"to\": 121}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"trailblazers\", \"from\": 137, \"to\": 150}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The event is the brainchild of former SOTT athlete Kester Edwards, who is a sports and development manager at Special Olympics International.\", \"from\": 222, \"to\": 363, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 332, \"end\": 348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.7028994481299e-20, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The event\", \"from\": 222, \"to\": 231}, {\"ngram\": \"the brainchild\", \"from\": 235, \"to\": 249}, {\"ngram\": \"former SOTT athlete Kester Edwards\", \"from\": 253, \"to\": 287}, {\"ngram\": \"a sports and development manager\", \"from\": 296, \"to\": 328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the course of three days, between November 8 and 10, Special Olympics athletes from across the region participated in aquathlon, beach football, beach cricket, beach volleyball, beach bocce, and open-water swimming.\", \"from\": 365, \"to\": 585, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 370, \"to\": 380}, {\"ngram\": \"three days\", \"from\": 384, \"to\": 394}, {\"ngram\": \"November\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 412}, {\"ngram\": \"the region\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 471}, {\"ngram\": \"aquathlon\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 497}, {\"ngram\": \"beach football\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 513}, {\"ngram\": \"beach cricket\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 528}, {\"ngram\": \"beach volleyball\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 546}, {\"ngram\": \"beach bocce\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 559}, {\"ngram\": \"open-water swimming\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 584}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The beach games offered the opportunity for athletes with intellectual disabilities to showcase their skills, compete against their peers, and build region-wide relationships.\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 762, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The beach games\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 602}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 626}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 639}, {\"ngram\": \"intellectual disabilities\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 670}, {\"ngram\": \"their skills\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 695}, {\"ngram\": \"their peers\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 724}, {\"ngram\": \"region-wide relationships\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 761}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is a\\u2026 crescendo of bringing all the plans together, that vision which Kester Edwards created [a long time] ago,\\\" Benjamin told theJamaica Observer.\", \"from\": 764, \"to\": 917, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 883, \"end\": 891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Benjamin\", \"score\": 0.5868512928871734, \"rank\": 0.6989084322923125, \"text\": \"Benjamin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4964182\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Benjamin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Benjamin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a\\u2026 crescendo\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 785}, {\"ngram\": \"all the plans\", \"from\": 798, \"to\": 811}, {\"ngram\": \"that vision\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 833}, {\"ngram\": \"Kester Edwards\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 854}, {\"ngram\": \"a long time\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 875}, {\"ngram\": \"theJamaica Observer\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 916}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are happy to be trailblazers and happy that it starts right here in the Caribbean.\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 1005, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"trailblazers\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 951}, {\"ngram\": \"the Caribbean\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1004}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And, we are going to write the template for this and make sure it can be exported and that other programmes can use local talent and local resources to showcase our Special Olympics Caribbean Beach Games,\\\" said the SOTT board chairman.\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1241, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1171, \"end\": 1187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.7028994481299e-20, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1188, \"end\": 1203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disney's_Caribbean_Beach_Resort\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caribbean Beach\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disney's_Caribbean_Beach_Resort\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disney's_Caribbean_Beach_Resort\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the template\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1045}, {\"ngram\": \"other programmes\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1113}, {\"ngram\": \"local talent\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1134}, {\"ngram\": \"local resources\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1154}, {\"ngram\": \"the SOTT board chairman\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Edwards, a Special Olympics International board representative, was on hand to see his dream come to fruition.\", \"from\": 1243, \"to\": 1353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1254, \"end\": 1270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.7028994481299e-20, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Ol